      <title>Bishops - Part 23: The Council in Trullo (conclusion)</title>
      <link>http://feeds.ancientfaith.com/~r/SpeakingTheTruth/~3/pjSvHQzbsPo/bishops_part_23_the_council_in_trullo_conclusion</link>
